# 🎓 Exam Duty Management System

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.10-blue)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Completed-brightgreen)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow)

A Python-based automation system designed to generate and manage **fair and efficient exam duty schedules** for academic institutions using structured data from Excel files.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

- 📊 Automatically generates exam duty schedules from teacher data
- ⚖️ Ensures fair workload distribution using rotation-based logic
- 🔁 Supports duty swapping between teachers
- 📁 Excel-based input and output support for easy integration
- 🧠 Clean and modular Python code structure
- ⚡ Fast and lightweight execution

---

## 🧠 How It Works

The system:
1. Reads teacher and exam duty data from an Excel file
2. Processes scheduling logic using rule-based assignment
3. Ensures fair rotation so no teacher is overburdened
4. Allows manual swapping of duties if required
5. Outputs updated duty schedule

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python 3
- Pandas
- OpenPyXL

